{"tid":197593,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果個人鍾意你，係咪幾忙都會搵你？","createTime":"2017-04-12T03:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T11:19:24.000Z","uid":92662,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"976621469f8b5897af7f4cef8410df3f6abe022f","tid":197593,"uid":92662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"一開頭大家都鍾意大家，但佢返工好忙，我又好需要人陪，最尾我頂唔順分開，後尾佢搵返我，但我無理佢，之後係某場合撞返佢，到我chur 返佢，傾左幾日，但佢忙嘅問題仲係度，最後又係不了了之，其實如果個男仔鍾意你，係咪幾忙都會搵你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟梗有機會再見到佢，諗梗要唔要主動搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3f4ad2084f76b41f0dfb302e6aa664a84cf03d","tid":197593,"uid":92662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"好想搵佢，會唔會好犯賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aad4d31d5c335c33333192e219073a218b539a3","tid":197593,"uid":15828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想搵佢，會唔會好犯賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都要你俾正常反應人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02874804b15a522aaca023450a6729774900c80e","tid":197593,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"有時做野真係唔方便 陪少陣你會死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa75a791592d0ce8f42850ffc2992176c281dc3","tid":197593,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"3e9a7eaf4a39eec5797bc46847cf030dad6fa761","tid":197593,"uid":4759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭大家都鍾意大家，但佢返工好忙，我又好需要人陪，最尾我頂唔順分開，後尾佢搵返我，但我無理佢，之後係某場合撞返佢，到我chur 返佢，傾左幾日，但佢忙嘅問題仲係度，最後又係不了了之，其實如果個男仔鍾意你，係咪幾忙都會搵你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟梗有機會再見到佢，諗梗要唔要主動搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾忙都會搵.<br />\n忙極點都一個鐘內都覆到msg 掛.<br />\n依家Whatsapp 仲要有電腦版<br />\n更加方便 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3579cd22e856fe70a4ce712858c153f72e4339","tid":197593,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"148599a130bcf18943c57239e7deac805faaa12f","tid":197593,"uid":93674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭大家都鍾意大家，但佢返工好忙，我又好需要人陪，最尾我頂唔順分開，後尾佢搵返我，但我無理佢，之後係某場合撞返佢，到我chur 返佢，傾左幾日，但佢忙嘅問題仲係度，最後又係不了了之，其實如果個男仔鍾意你，係咪幾忙都會搵你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟梗有機會再見到佢，諗梗要唔要主動搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾犯賤<br />\n點忙都好，wtsapp幾句都唔係好難姐<br />\n你地始終分開過，而分開嘅原因都仲係到<br />\n咁如果無人願意退一步嘅話，都好快會再分開"},{"pid":"0db3d509bf0867daa45d56bc31210ad81d936bab","tid":197593,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"166c78de5509a8296e58f653859668ecb8bf5abd","tid":197593,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭大家都鍾意大家，但佢返工好忙，我又好需要人陪，最尾我頂唔順分開，後尾佢搵返我，但我無理佢，之後係某場合撞返佢，到我chur 返佢，傾左幾日，但佢忙嘅問題仲係度，最後又係不了了之，其實如果個男仔鍾意你，係咪幾忙都會搵你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟梗有機會再見到佢，諗梗要唔要主動搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你冇理佢係on9"},{"pid":"a679fa004ab17f3bda6779625a481288011c0a29","tid":197593,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"忙又點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c651700854c2b622c20d34d9cee6e83bc83339e","tid":197593,"uid":92662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時做野真係唔方便 陪少陣你會死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但一日WhatsApp 可能淨係傾十句左右，一個月見一次喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bd884952809010247f28bcbc8e107db95a2c24","tid":197593,"uid":67026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/113659_3701867dd660806fc8cde6d666d64f26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F113659_3701867dd660806fc8cde6d666d64f26.jpg&h=40313835&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d50c318e4b1d38db16d69edb35146a193bad1247","tid":197593,"uid":90149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"046079b7a13ac604e6fb5eb53a738695d4e3c62b","tid":197593,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一開頭大家都鍾意大家，但佢返工好忙，我又好需要人陪，最尾我頂唔順分開，後尾佢搵返我，但我無理佢，之後係某場合撞返佢，到我chur 返佢，傾左幾日，但佢忙嘅問題仲係度，最後又係不了了之，其實如果個男仔鍾意你，係咪幾忙都會搵你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟梗有機會再見到佢，諗梗要唔要主動搵佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都幾犯賤<br />\n點忙都好，wtsapp幾句都唔係好難姐<br />\n你地始終分開過，而分開嘅原因都仲係到<br />\n咁如果無人願意退一步嘅話，都好快會再分開</blockquote><br />\nExact