 />\n又好似真係好少<br />\n至少一星期一次囉😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想係一個禮拜一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13e0324f5bb3c7284ca0f87c17254959aec069f","tid":197593,"uid":92662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有時做野真係唔方便 陪少陣你會死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但一日WhatsApp 可能淨係傾十句左右，一個月見一次喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你講清楚d先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁真係少得太過份 <br />\n你有無了解過佢一直拍拖係咪咁 定同你先係</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，唔同圈子，唔知佢之前拍拖係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢做邊行?</blockquote><br />\n佢做Bank"},{"pid":"eeeeb55553555abf344e0b7b584a42edc69dc694","tid":197593,"uid":5518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"有心覆，食飯點都會覆一覆表示今日好忙<br />\n如果佢同你相處冇壓力的話收工一定會搵<br />\n如果冇咩點搵諗下你地相處有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a89910c818743734e57ee464f34639dd277b416","tid":197593,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:10:25.000Z","msg":"你咁撚煩 搵你咪等於找屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾我就唔搵你啦"},{"pid":"409b5f26be8049c9113e0af19e81338f939472d9","tid":197593,"uid":92662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>忙又點搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc